FILE: dispatch.rs
MOD: broker/state
ROLE: Stanza dispatch — resolves destination, resolves mentions, routes to delivery engine or updates presence
EP: dispatch_stanza
STAB: volatile
INV:
  - dispatch_stanza resolves ALL mentions before calling deliver() — fail-fast on AmbiguousMention
  - If any mention is AmbiguousMention, the entire send is rejected — no partial delivery
  - CrossProjectChannel path returns early after deliver_to_cross_project_channel — does NOT fall through to deliver()
  - validate_target=true for HTTP path (agent must exist); validate_target=false for WS path (agent may not yet be registered)
  - DispatchError variants: TargetNotFound, DeliveryFailed, CrossProjectDenied, CrossProjectNotFound, AmbiguousMention
  - Cross-project channel auth check fires before channel existence check — 403 before 404
LOOK: resolve_destination; resolve_mentions; Destination enum variants; DispatchError variants
CHK: arch fitness after adding new DispatchError variants; cargo test dispatch
CNTR: broker/state::dispatch_stanza depends_on stanza/types::resolve_destination
CNTR: broker/state::dispatch_stanza depends_on stanza/types::resolve_mentions
DEPS-ON: broker/state; broker/delivery; stanza/types; db/repository
